ObjectPropertyAssertion(<http://www.semanticweb.org/nitza/ontologies/2025/10/untitled-ontology-es#tienePerfilAccion> <http://www.semanticweb.org/nitza/ontologies/2025/10/untitled-ontology-es#Aspart> <http://www.semanticweb.org/nitza/ontologies/2025/10/untitled-ontology-es#acc_rapida>)
